//// scale
scale waa zoom in io zoom out default 1 buu sitaa -hadu galo waa zoom out(yareyn) 

////transform 

+ hadu noqdana waa zoom in (so weyneyn)
transform waa halke ku keydsanyihin scale io waxyabo kalo animation ah

///rotate

waa marka rabto waxan inaa kala gediso ama siduu uyaalo wax kabadashid

////translate

wa marka dhaqdhaqaajineyso elementigaga ina meel ka wado oo meel geyso kale

// skew

inaa janjeer udhigto elementigaga

//hover waxu ku xiranyahay mouse ka marku kortago uun bu shaqeeyas